{{!
    @template tool_fix_delete_modules/task_diagnosis

    The template displays the diagnosis of one course_delete_module task. It contains a heading and a table of 'symptoms'.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * title string - The title of the adhoc task (including taskid and course module id(s)).
    * table string - HTML table listing the list of issues (aka 'symtoms') for this course_delete_module task.
    * button string - HTML form/button.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "title": "Diagnosis taskid(4321) (cmid:5432, instanceid: 1342)",
        "table": "<table><tr><td> ....</td></tr></table>",
        "button": "<form>...</form>"
    }
}}
<div class="fix-diagnosis">
    <h4 class="fix-diagnosis-heading">{{title}}</h4>
    {{{table}}}
    {{{button}}}
</div>
